sial notion of grammarians as the guardians of the divine wisdom, the present study pivots on one of its greatest embodiment: Ibn al-Sarrāj's concept of the Wisdom of Arabs.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aCatenae. 0aManuscripts, Greek. 4aIslam. 4aKoran & Sacred Writings. 4aReligion. 7aREFERENCE / Catalogs.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2021 Englishz978311075419308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2021z9783110753974oZDB-23-DGF08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertGorgias Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z97831107433020 cprintz978146324260240uhttps://doi.org/10.31826/9781463242619zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781463242619zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781463242619/original  a978-3-11-074330-2 Gorgias Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-074335-7 DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075419-3 EBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2021 Englishb2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGFb2021  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-GOA